reviewText: it was a great dvd it was everything and more iam glad i got it it was worth it m

hello, bounty hunter chapman and family. the fact that you were honored for being crime fighters, very dedicated, tough, down and dirty crime fighters recognized by the hawaiian house of reps was very intriguing to both watch and listen to. if there were tickets to that event i would buy one in your honor. to the chapmans!!!! we trust!!!!

RACIST...REALLY....RACIST, GIVE ME A BREAK HE'S NOTHING COMPARE TO ME. I'M A SOUTHERN REDNECK WHO COULD WALK CIRCLES AROUND THE BEST HE COULD COME UP WITH. PEOPLE STOP WHINNING THE "N" WORD IS NOT THE WORST WORD A MAN COULD COME UP WITH!!!
Very good  yes if you are a DOG fan  well done

The product was received in the timeframe provided and in new excellent condition.
I do have one complaint about the DVD's format, I find it annoying that the sequences do not automatically advance to the next story. It's odd how you have to choose & press play to view the next story line. All other shows continously run thru the end of the DVD.

We have a 5 year old grandson who is "In Love" with Dog The Bounty Hunter and family. He absolutely loved receiving this package. We received it just a couple of days after ordering (which is simple with Amazon). I have used Amazon frequently for items I cannot find in local stores and have been very happy with the results. Highly recommend both!!
Before you buy this product please google Chapman and then think about whether you want to support someone who casually uses the N word.

Well, finally us Australian's can catch up with Dog & the Posse by watching Dog The Bounty Hunter: The Best Of Season 4 - Can't wait for Season 5 to be released now...since it won't be on our screens until this time next year... & that's only if we're lucky!!
We are all so fortunate to have Dog and crew back, all good words aren't enough to write a proper review!!!  Marjy Outlaw

GREAT WORK TO DOG, BETH AND ALL (ABSOLUTLY ALL) !!
It was all that I had expected and more. Love him, the series and  his family, moral values and kindnesses without being too judgmental.
If you like his show and do not suscribe to prime you will like this DVD if you like Bounty hunter's
I love his heart to catch them and try to inspire them to change their lives for the better. His life experiences give him credibility with the people he helps.
Was a gift for my son,he loves it! It;s action packed and he watches it often. Will order other ones.
The wife loves this series so I got it for her it's on too early for her so she has all these dog the bounty hunter to watch.

At the end of the day, as much as I love Dog and that motley crew of ever-growing bounty hunters at Da Kine Bail Bonds, I've got to recommend that people avoid this disc for much the same reason why I suggested avoiding the Criss Angel best-of discs recently. You're basically paying $20 for a few minutes of extra footage. No commentaries, no still biographies or anything else to justify the purchase. It's a shame, because especially in the case of this particular season, these discs could be so much better than they are.
that season was very different because already people knows them and it was hard to be undercover so I love the new opening and seeing the little kid grow
Son has long standing love for The Dog.  My son is handicapped so this keeps him entertained for long periods of time.  I don't think anyone love's Dog more than him.
Excellent as always!! Dog, Beth and their family never fail to entertain their audience. I'm definitely buying their other DVD sets!
Love the show glad we were able to find some of the series. Enjoy watching it during those times when nothing seems to be on TV
I would not recommend this product.  Look for the lost first episode because its a lot more fun to see.
